WEBVTT

00:17.000 --> 00:21.760
A MONTH LATER

00:28.360 --> 00:29.320
Stop crying.

00:29.400 --> 00:30.720
I'll cut out your tongues
if you keep crying.

00:31.240 --> 00:32.080
Hear me?

00:38.640 --> 00:39.480
Who is that?

00:40.040 --> 00:41.160
I'm a pig slaughterer.

00:41.680 --> 00:44.040
Pig slaughterer? There are no pigs here.

00:45.800 --> 00:47.600
Aren't there three right in front of me?

01:34.800 --> 01:36.960
Ever since a "Beauty Slaughterer"
appeared in Jizhou,

01:37.040 --> 01:39.440
ladies love to carry knives
when they go out.

01:39.520 --> 01:40.920
Says it wards off evils.

01:41.000 --> 01:42.280
Isn't that right?

01:42.360 --> 01:43.920
Nowadays, these young ladies

01:44.000 --> 01:45.400
actually believe this.

01:45.480 --> 01:46.680
Anyone going on a long journey

01:46.760 --> 01:48.240
all dresses up like this.

01:48.760 --> 01:49.720
Look.

01:49.800 --> 01:52.120
Now for those human traffickers, robbers,

01:52.200 --> 01:54.800
village bullies, and local thugs,

01:54.880 --> 01:55.960
what they fear most

01:56.040 --> 01:58.480
is meeting a pretty girl
carrying a butchering knife.

02:00.120 --> 02:01.280
Young lady.

02:01.880 --> 02:03.400
-You look so nice.
-Let me see it.

02:11.400 --> 02:12.880
Beauty Slaughterer!

02:12.960 --> 02:14.000
Quick, run!

02:18.440 --> 02:20.720
Thank you. Thank you, Beauty Slaughterer!

02:21.800 --> 02:23.280
Look, they are all imitating her.

02:23.800 --> 02:24.920
Stop talking nonsense.

02:25.000 --> 02:26.240
If you happen to meet the real deal,

02:26.320 --> 02:27.960
it is only fair to get you
castrated on the spot.

02:28.480 --> 02:29.560
-Lecher!
-Let's try over there.

02:29.640 --> 02:30.920
Filthy language!

02:31.000 --> 02:32.040
Ignore them.

02:32.120 --> 02:33.080
Look at this.

02:39.240 --> 02:40.760
MEDICINE

02:41.400 --> 02:42.520
Where is Fan Changning?

02:42.600 --> 02:43.920
Is there a Fan Changning?

02:45.240 --> 02:46.280
No such name.

02:47.120 --> 02:48.160
Next.

02:49.600 --> 02:50.440
Ning.

02:51.160 --> 02:52.400
Where on earth are you?

02:53.960 --> 02:55.560
I saved so many people.

02:56.160 --> 02:57.680
Why can't I still find you?

02:57.760 --> 02:58.600
MISSING PERSONS

02:58.680 --> 03:02.080
Yan Zheng, if only you were here.

03:02.760 --> 03:04.000
The world is so vast.

03:05.200 --> 03:06.800
Where are you two?

03:17.160 --> 03:18.000
Hey!

03:18.520 --> 03:19.360
Stand right there!

03:20.000 --> 03:21.160
You just won't listen, right?

03:23.520 --> 03:25.520
Told you not to go that way, right?

03:26.040 --> 03:27.760
Go the other way. Understand?

03:32.240 --> 03:33.200
Ning!

03:33.280 --> 03:34.560
Stop!

03:45.600 --> 03:46.760
Don't hit my daddy!

03:46.840 --> 03:48.160
Don't hit my daddy!

03:49.400 --> 03:50.240
Who are you?

03:50.320 --> 03:51.760
Why are you hitting me?

03:55.040 --> 03:56.000
Are you okay?

03:57.800 --> 03:58.680
Sorry.

03:59.200 --> 04:00.280
I thought you were a human trafficker.

04:00.360 --> 04:01.520
Human trafficker?

04:01.600 --> 04:03.720
I think you're the human trafficker!

04:04.360 --> 04:05.600
I'm going to report you
to the authorities!

04:05.680 --> 04:07.000
I'm going to report you
to the authorities!

05:35.240 --> 05:39.880
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

05:39.960 --> 05:42.640
EPISODE 20

05:47.840 --> 05:50.720
BAXIA

05:50.800 --> 05:52.280
Once we cross this stone,

05:52.360 --> 05:53.920
we're on my Sui family's territory.

05:55.240 --> 05:57.360
Common folks all call this place Baxia.

05:58.000 --> 05:59.720
According to the legend,
the dragon had nine sons.

05:59.800 --> 06:01.320
One of them resembled a turtle.

06:01.840 --> 06:03.640
Immensely strong, it could
churn rivers and seas.

06:04.160 --> 06:06.000
It was only subdued by Da Yu
when he tamed the floods.

06:07.920 --> 06:09.960
Father bestowed
this strategic location on me.

06:10.560 --> 06:12.320
I renamed it as Baxia.

06:13.400 --> 06:16.520
Hoping this land can live up to its name,

06:17.040 --> 06:17.880
being indestructible.

06:19.280 --> 06:21.560
Isn't this just a big turtle?

06:24.600 --> 06:27.160
The dragon's son is just a big turtle.

06:29.080 --> 06:30.320
I was wasting effort
on an unreceptive audience.

06:31.680 --> 06:34.000
-Keep up.
-The terrain here is so low.

06:34.080 --> 06:35.520
What if there's a flood?

06:39.760 --> 06:40.600
We're here.

06:49.680 --> 06:55.680
SUI

06:58.560 --> 07:00.960
Welcome, Your Highness, back to the manor.

07:08.520 --> 07:10.760
Welcome, Your Highness, back to the manor.

07:10.840 --> 07:13.440
SOARING WINDS, UNBOUNDED SPIRIT

07:14.040 --> 07:16.440
Welcome, Your Highness, back to the manor.

07:23.840 --> 07:26.480
Take my friends here
to the guest rooms. Treat them well.

07:26.560 --> 07:28.120
Yes. This way.

07:28.200 --> 07:29.080
-Thank you, Your Highness.
-Thank you, Your Highness.

07:30.880 --> 07:31.720
Let's go.

07:35.400 --> 07:37.600
‎SOARING WINDS, UNBOUNDED SPIRIT

07:39.240 --> 07:41.000
Let's go. What are you doing?

07:41.080 --> 07:42.880
You really are the son of Prince Changxin?

07:44.600 --> 07:46.800
Yes. What did you think?

07:48.440 --> 07:50.000
I thought you were lying to me.

07:57.880 --> 07:58.760
Brother!

07:58.840 --> 08:00.080
EVER VICTORIOUS

08:00.160 --> 08:01.200
Yuanqing.

08:01.840 --> 08:02.720
Brother!

08:03.600 --> 08:04.680
How have you been recently?

08:05.200 --> 08:06.520
I've been well.

08:06.600 --> 08:08.000
You have been through a lot.

08:22.680 --> 08:23.800
I have something to discuss with you.

08:23.880 --> 08:25.720
-Settle them in for some rest.
-Yes.

08:28.400 --> 08:29.440
This way, please.

08:30.640 --> 08:31.800
Come.

08:34.240 --> 08:35.799
Come, let's talk inside.

08:42.200 --> 08:43.440
Scouts reported this morning.

08:44.039 --> 08:47.120
Xie Zheng led a surprise attack
on our Chongzhou grain route last night.

08:47.200 --> 08:50.280
I fear Father won't be able to hold out
at the Lucheng front.

08:50.360 --> 08:53.720
How did Xie Zheng, without anyone knowing,
penetrate deep into Chongzhou?

08:54.480 --> 08:55.320
How many men did he bring?

08:56.360 --> 08:57.680
No more than a hundred cavalry.

09:01.120 --> 09:02.120
Damn it.

09:02.800 --> 09:05.240
Repairing this grain route
will take at least over a month.

09:05.320 --> 09:08.080
Before, Brother mentioned sending men
to guard the grain route.

09:08.640 --> 09:10.200
But Father rejected it.

09:11.240 --> 09:12.280
What a pity.

09:16.240 --> 09:17.080
By the way.

09:17.160 --> 09:19.600
Who were those two just now?

09:22.440 --> 09:24.880
The older one, she's my woman.

09:25.760 --> 09:28.800
The little one is a big surprise.

09:38.960 --> 09:41.360
DECREE OF BENEVOLENT GOVERNANCE

09:43.240 --> 09:45.400
I thought he would get rid of the mother
and keep the child.

09:45.920 --> 09:47.760
Turns out it's the opposite.

09:49.080 --> 09:50.720
So soft-hearted.

09:51.560 --> 09:53.160
Never expected

09:53.240 --> 09:55.280
that Brother is the same as Marquis Wu'an.

09:58.080 --> 10:00.960
Only you are so heartless.

10:03.800 --> 10:05.040
Me, heartless?

10:09.160 --> 10:10.720
As long as you stay with me,

10:11.240 --> 10:12.760
I can give you anything you want.

10:14.920 --> 10:15.920
Then I…

10:17.080 --> 10:19.960
want Xie Zheng and Fan Changyu's heads.

10:22.320 --> 10:23.160
Deal.

10:24.040 --> 10:25.320
Agreed.

10:36.680 --> 10:38.200
Do you still hate me now?

10:45.600 --> 10:47.200
I don't want to overthink now.

10:48.640 --> 10:49.880
After tonight,

10:49.960 --> 10:52.080
I'll decide whether to hate you or not.

11:01.280 --> 11:04.560
YANZHOU MILITARY CAMP

11:10.080 --> 11:12.320
You've worked hard for this strike.

11:12.920 --> 11:14.720
Since when are you so polite to me?

11:14.800 --> 11:16.080
How will you repay me?

11:16.920 --> 11:17.880
Forget what I said.

11:18.800 --> 11:20.520
As for He Jingyuan,

11:20.600 --> 11:23.240
last time during the Lin'an siege,
he solved your predicament.

11:23.760 --> 11:26.240
This time, you attacked the grain route
to give him a breather.

11:26.320 --> 11:27.680
Consider it even.

11:27.760 --> 11:28.840
Oh right, the package.

11:32.560 --> 11:34.840
Someone entrusted me to give this to you.

11:47.600 --> 11:48.440
Candy?

11:49.400 --> 11:51.120
Aren't you the one
who hates sweets the most?

11:53.760 --> 11:56.040
What's wrong? Won't even let me touch it?

12:00.560 --> 12:03.440
DIVORCE LETTER

12:11.520 --> 12:12.760
FAN CHANGYU, WIFE, NATIVE OF JIZHOU
YAN ZHENG, HUSBAND, NATIVE OF CHONGZHOU

12:12.840 --> 12:14.120
HEREBY DIVORCE BY CONSENT
NO HEIRS, NO SHARED ESTATE

12:14.200 --> 12:15.520
FREE TO REMARRY

12:15.600 --> 12:17.000
TO PROTECT EACH OTHER'S REPUTATION
LET THIS LETTER SERVE AS EVIDENCE

12:17.080 --> 12:18.840
SIGNATURE FROM THE WIFE: FAN CHANGYU
SIGNATURE FROM THE HUSBAND

12:22.240 --> 12:23.640
We owe each other nothing anymore.

12:25.560 --> 12:26.400
That's fine.

12:33.920 --> 12:35.280
Where did this bag come from?

12:36.480 --> 12:38.920
Mr. Zhao pulled strings
through layers of connections.

12:40.480 --> 12:41.640
He was also conscripted.

12:42.680 --> 12:43.760
But don't worry.

12:43.840 --> 12:45.120
At most, he will only know me.

12:45.880 --> 12:47.160
He won't know you are here.

12:53.280 --> 12:54.360
Tell them.

12:55.280 --> 12:56.720
Don't let him go to the front lines.

12:57.240 --> 12:58.720
Assign him to the military supply camp.

12:59.800 --> 13:00.640
Alright.

13:05.560 --> 13:08.160
Marquis. The Chongzhou Scout
delivered a declaration of war to you.

13:10.120 --> 13:11.360
TO TRAITOR XIE

13:25.920 --> 13:27.640
Isn't this what I drew?

13:30.800 --> 13:32.200
Sui Yuanqing said

13:32.720 --> 13:34.080
my daughter is in his hands.

13:35.480 --> 13:36.720
Your daughter?

13:39.560 --> 13:41.080
Fan Changning has fallen into his hands.

14:00.360 --> 14:02.200
JIZHOU PREFECTURAL OFFICE

14:02.280 --> 14:03.200
JIZHOU PREFECTURAL OFFICE

14:03.280 --> 14:04.120
Here they come.

14:04.720 --> 14:06.280
Come here. Come here.

14:06.360 --> 14:08.320
-Mother, I miss you so much.
-My dear.

14:09.920 --> 14:13.240
Your Honor, I heard it was
the Beauty Slaughterer who saved my son,

14:13.320 --> 14:14.880
yet she's the one in prison instead?

14:14.960 --> 14:16.680
She has merit, not guilt!

14:16.760 --> 14:18.800
That's right. Release her, please.
She saved us.

14:18.880 --> 14:20.680
-She has merit, not guilt!
-Right!

14:38.880 --> 14:40.160
Mrs. Fan.

14:41.480 --> 14:42.960
You don't need to force yourself.

14:45.680 --> 14:46.800
Father and Mother said

14:47.520 --> 14:48.720
you must still eat,

14:49.240 --> 14:50.280
still sleep.

14:51.560 --> 14:52.800
Even if the sky falls,

14:53.320 --> 14:54.560
a person still has to live.

14:59.720 --> 15:01.240
You clearly know I can protect you.

15:01.760 --> 15:03.160
I can take you away from here.

15:04.840 --> 15:06.320
But why won't you?

15:22.560 --> 15:23.880
It has been two months already.

15:26.280 --> 15:28.400
I still haven't been able to find Ning.

15:33.720 --> 15:36.160
I don't know where else I can go.

15:43.760 --> 15:45.320
I'm really useless.

15:48.360 --> 15:51.920
I don't even know where Ning is suffering.

16:18.920 --> 16:21.960
JIZHOU PREFECTURAL OFFICE

16:31.720 --> 16:34.160
THE CASE IS CLEAR

16:36.040 --> 16:37.240
You said

16:37.800 --> 16:39.880
my parents were killed
by mountain bandits.

16:41.400 --> 16:42.520
What you said,

16:43.960 --> 16:44.960
is it true?

16:47.240 --> 16:48.160
What do you mean?

16:49.720 --> 16:51.440
Grandpa told me,

16:52.920 --> 16:54.640
the day before my parents died,

16:54.720 --> 16:55.800
they asked him to take care of us.

16:57.040 --> 16:58.480
They knew they were going to die.

16:58.560 --> 16:59.520
Why didn't they hide?

17:00.640 --> 17:02.880
Why could they still arrange
the family's property

17:02.960 --> 17:04.240
and then go to die?

17:04.960 --> 17:07.160
Were they really killed
by mountain bandits?

17:08.240 --> 17:09.240
Lord Li.

17:10.920 --> 17:12.440
I want to see the case files.

17:13.319 --> 17:15.960
It seems these files
were indeed altered before.

17:17.880 --> 17:20.000
Grandfather sent an urgent letter,
saying this matter

17:20.079 --> 17:22.319
is likely related
to the Jinzhou massacre 17 years ago.

17:24.000 --> 17:25.079
The Jinzhou massacre?

17:34.440 --> 17:35.600
What?

17:35.680 --> 17:37.800
You already took ten taels of silver.
That's not enough?

17:38.680 --> 17:39.640
Enough, enough.

17:39.720 --> 17:42.360
I wanted to say if I had known
she was the Beauty Slaughterer,

17:42.440 --> 17:43.640
I definitely wouldn't have blamed her.

17:44.320 --> 17:45.160
My Lord.

17:45.240 --> 17:46.880
We beg you, release her.
She is our savior!

17:46.960 --> 17:48.280
-She has merit, not guilt!
-True!

17:48.360 --> 17:49.920
-That's right, my Lord.
-Please release her, our savior!

17:50.000 --> 17:50.840
Our savior is here!

17:50.920 --> 17:52.240
-Our savior is out!
-She is out!

17:54.040 --> 17:55.400
-Thank you, our savior!
-Thank you!

17:55.480 --> 17:56.560
Thank you!

17:56.640 --> 17:58.160
-Thank you!
-Our savior, what's wrong?

17:58.240 --> 17:59.760
Why are you crying?

18:02.640 --> 18:03.760
My younger sister

18:05.800 --> 18:07.000
is also missing.

18:07.760 --> 18:09.720
I still don't know where she is now.

18:11.320 --> 18:13.520
We all have moments of carelessness.

18:14.240 --> 18:16.000
I, too, because of carelessness,

18:16.080 --> 18:17.760
lost my own daughter.

18:18.360 --> 18:19.800
Everyone makes mistakes.

18:19.880 --> 18:22.240
Your sister will definitely be found.

18:22.320 --> 18:24.000
-Kindness will be rewarded.
-Yes.

18:24.080 --> 18:25.120
-That's right.
-She will be found.

18:25.200 --> 18:26.520
A mistake is a mistake.

18:28.520 --> 18:30.800
Losing a child because of
my own carelessness,

18:31.320 --> 18:33.440
how can I easily forgive myself?

18:34.720 --> 18:36.200
If I don't remember this time,

18:36.760 --> 18:38.680
I'll lose her again next time.

18:48.080 --> 18:49.680
I should also learn my lesson.

18:58.480 --> 18:59.360
Mrs. Fan.

19:00.680 --> 19:02.880
Didn't you want to read
your parents' case files?

19:04.240 --> 19:05.360
I found them.

19:07.360 --> 19:10.360
YAMEN

19:17.600 --> 19:18.680
Ms. Fan.

19:18.760 --> 19:20.160
These are your family's murder case files.

19:23.880 --> 19:26.200
Will you be affected
by my investigation of this case?

19:36.960 --> 19:39.240
There are some characters
I don't quite recognize.

19:41.200 --> 19:42.240
Which characters?

19:44.160 --> 19:45.200
This one.

19:45.280 --> 19:46.120
THE 12TH MONTH, 16TH YEAR OF ZHENGPING
CASE OF BANDIT MURDER: FAN ERNIU AND LIHUA

19:46.200 --> 19:47.080
This one. This one.

19:47.760 --> 19:50.280
I know these ones.
The rest is unknown to me.

19:52.800 --> 19:53.960
Then let me read it for you.

19:54.040 --> 19:55.040
Thank you.

19:59.040 --> 20:00.680
"Sixteenth year of Yongping, October.

20:02.480 --> 20:05.960
Fan Erniu of Lin'an Town
traveled with his wife.

20:06.960 --> 20:09.120
They encountered misfortune on the road.

20:09.200 --> 20:12.000
Fan Erniu, male, 45.

20:12.520 --> 20:14.240
Clad in a gray short coat.

20:14.800 --> 20:17.800
Multiple stab wounds
on chest and abdomen found.

20:18.640 --> 20:20.200
This case's evidence is conclusive.

20:21.080 --> 20:23.040
We have already dispatched people
to apprehend the true culprit."

20:27.840 --> 20:29.000
I thought

20:29.560 --> 20:31.080
I could find clues from the case files.

20:32.320 --> 20:35.760
So my parents were indeed killed
by mountain bandits.

20:37.320 --> 20:39.720
Even if it wasn't those ones
from Qingfeng Stronghold,

20:39.800 --> 20:41.480
it would have been other bandits.

20:42.840 --> 20:43.800
Ms. Fan.

20:44.680 --> 20:46.000
What's past cannot be mended.

20:46.520 --> 20:47.720
The future can still be pursued.

20:51.480 --> 20:52.400
Mrs. Fan.

20:53.280 --> 20:54.120
This is your package.

20:54.200 --> 20:55.520
Check if anything is missing.

21:02.880 --> 21:03.720
DIVORCE LETTER

21:08.120 --> 21:09.200
HARMONY AND PROSPERITY FOR ALL

21:09.280 --> 21:10.920
What are your plans for the future?

21:12.280 --> 21:13.720
Find Ning quickly.

21:14.360 --> 21:16.400
Auntie is still in Lin'an,
waiting for me to bring her back.

21:20.280 --> 21:21.160
And Yan Zheng.

21:22.640 --> 21:24.240
Whether he is dead or alive,

21:24.760 --> 21:25.680
I will find him.

21:28.560 --> 21:29.600
In that case,

21:30.360 --> 21:32.000
why not stay here?

21:32.080 --> 21:33.200
Let me help you find Ning.

21:35.080 --> 21:36.240
The battle is imminent.

21:36.760 --> 21:38.200
You must be very busy.

21:38.280 --> 21:40.400
This is my family matter.
I won't trouble you with it.

21:43.520 --> 21:44.360
Then…

21:44.880 --> 21:46.640
If there's anything you need,

21:46.720 --> 21:48.160
just ask me.
No need to keep it to youreself.

21:49.600 --> 21:51.640
Thank you for your sincere help.

21:51.720 --> 21:52.840
Previously, you paid

21:53.360 --> 21:55.000
ten taels of silver for me.

21:55.080 --> 21:56.560
I got them ready.

21:57.240 --> 21:58.800
A while ago,

21:58.880 --> 22:00.000
I helped Lin'an Yamen

22:00.080 --> 22:01.560
destroy several human trafficking dens.

22:02.320 --> 22:03.840
It wasn't anything great,

22:03.920 --> 22:05.600
but they still gave me silver as a reward.

22:06.960 --> 22:08.000
It's at the post station.

22:08.080 --> 22:09.560
I will bring it to you once I return.

22:11.640 --> 22:12.520
Alright.

22:13.320 --> 22:14.600
Attendants.

22:14.680 --> 22:16.080
Escort Mrs. Fan back.

22:16.720 --> 22:17.560
This way, please.

22:24.920 --> 22:27.280
Should we inform Lord He
about Mrs. Fan's matter?

22:27.360 --> 22:29.000
Even Ms. Fan knows a battle is imminent.

22:29.080 --> 22:30.440
No need to disturb military morale.

22:31.280 --> 22:32.960
After all, the master
is the commander-in-chief.

22:33.040 --> 22:34.880
We shouldn't disturb him, should we?

22:38.920 --> 22:40.880
My Lord, an urgent letter
from the Grand Tutor.

22:50.600 --> 22:51.920
After the grain route was destroyed,

22:52.000 --> 22:53.840
Prince Changxin indeed couldn't hold on.

22:54.360 --> 22:55.920
He retreated to Hongdaokou.

22:57.120 --> 22:59.160
Next to come is the monsoon season.

22:59.240 --> 23:00.520
Streams change course.

23:00.600 --> 23:02.080
Mountain roads are hard to travel.

23:02.160 --> 23:05.080
If Prince Changxin sends troops south,

23:05.160 --> 23:06.800
he will inevitably pass through Baxia.

23:10.760 --> 23:12.560
It's time to visit He Jingyuan.

23:13.400 --> 23:15.560
Baxia is at the downstream of Wu River.

23:15.640 --> 23:17.800
When the monsoon season comes,

23:18.320 --> 23:20.560
General He can take men to the upstream

23:20.640 --> 23:22.640
and build a dam secretly.

23:22.720 --> 23:24.800
Marquis will act as bait alone downstream.

23:25.400 --> 23:27.000
If the rebels fall for the trap,

23:27.080 --> 23:28.640
they will suffer heavy losses.

23:28.720 --> 23:30.600
This plan can lift the siege of Lucheng.

23:33.240 --> 23:34.600
A flooding strategy.

23:35.280 --> 23:36.760
This plan, though clever,

23:37.800 --> 23:41.040
will be risking Marquis' life.

23:41.560 --> 23:43.600
If anything goes wrong…

23:44.800 --> 23:45.920
I feel I am not enough of the bait.

23:46.640 --> 23:49.400
The cunning Sui Yuanqing
won't take it easily.

23:52.080 --> 23:53.480
If General He trusts me,

23:54.000 --> 23:55.760
before the main Yanzhou army arrives,

23:56.680 --> 23:58.680
please give me a thousand men.

23:59.280 --> 24:00.880
A thousand men?

24:00.960 --> 24:02.360
Do you know

24:02.440 --> 24:03.800
Sui Yuanqing

24:03.880 --> 24:06.000
has 200,000 soldiers at Baxia?

24:06.640 --> 24:09.200
It will be hard to escape
for too many soldiers.

24:17.120 --> 24:18.680
This is a plan to lure the enemy.

24:19.280 --> 24:22.480
You are peerless in wisdom and bravery.

24:23.120 --> 24:25.000
Good, I agree.

24:26.360 --> 24:28.600
Thank you, General He.

24:28.680 --> 24:31.080
If we can lift the siege of Lucheng

24:31.600 --> 24:33.080
and protect Jizhou,

24:33.160 --> 24:35.920
it is I who should thank you both.

24:39.280 --> 24:40.480
-Thank you, General.
-Thank you, General.

24:43.480 --> 24:44.320
General.

24:45.360 --> 24:48.120
I came here this time
with one more request.

24:48.200 --> 24:49.080
Speak.

24:51.880 --> 24:52.720
I wish to keep it between us.

24:54.320 --> 24:55.480
You all may leave.

24:55.560 --> 24:56.520
Yes.

24:59.800 --> 25:01.160
This way, please.

25:07.600 --> 25:08.520
General He.

25:09.160 --> 25:11.880
I planned straight for Baxia this time

25:12.440 --> 25:13.480
for another reason. To rescue one person.

25:14.320 --> 25:17.120
Prince Changxin's son kidnapped
my wife's younger sister.

25:17.640 --> 25:18.800
I must rescue her.

25:18.880 --> 25:20.240
Your wife's younger sister?

25:21.400 --> 25:22.840
The younger Fan girl was captured?

25:29.000 --> 25:31.720
It seems General He already knows
my relationship with the Fan family.

25:34.080 --> 25:35.680
I dare to ask.

25:35.760 --> 25:38.280
The Fan couple's murder case last year.

25:38.800 --> 25:40.520
Do you know anything about it?

25:42.840 --> 25:44.480
A bit too direct, aren't you?

25:52.920 --> 25:53.800
General He?

25:59.080 --> 26:00.200
So,

26:00.720 --> 26:05.200
Fan Erniu was once my comrade
and friend in the same camp.

26:07.160 --> 26:09.600
Before his death, he gave me a letter.

26:10.280 --> 26:12.160
He told me to deliver it
to Chancellor Wei,

26:12.240 --> 26:16.120
and advised me absolutely
not to open or read it.

26:16.840 --> 26:18.320
So,

26:18.400 --> 26:22.240
in order to make Chancellor Wei believe
you were still loyal to him,

26:22.760 --> 26:24.840
you killed a former friend?

26:30.880 --> 26:33.480
No. Brother Fan took his own life.

26:34.800 --> 26:37.440
But it was after I arrived.

26:37.520 --> 26:40.760
You could also say
it was forced by my presence.

26:43.600 --> 26:45.200
If I hadn't gone there,

26:45.840 --> 26:47.680
Chancellor Wei would have
sent someone else.

26:48.560 --> 26:50.080
By that time,

26:50.160 --> 26:52.920
it would have been "uprooting the grass
and destroying the roots."

26:58.000 --> 26:59.960
Since ancient times,
loyalty and honor rarely align.

27:01.440 --> 27:02.760
It's not entirely your fault.

27:03.600 --> 27:05.640
But the old friend is gone.

27:06.160 --> 27:10.160
I feel guilty in my heart.

27:12.120 --> 27:13.600
The Fan girls' father

27:14.120 --> 27:15.360
wasn't called Fan Erniu, was he?

27:15.880 --> 27:17.360
What was his real name?

27:18.280 --> 27:21.240
And what position did he hold
under the Chancellor?

27:21.840 --> 27:22.880
Marquis.

27:22.960 --> 27:24.480
This matter,

27:25.000 --> 27:26.680
I absolutely cannot tell you.

27:27.800 --> 27:32.520
At least let’s wait until
the two Fan sisters are safe.

27:32.600 --> 27:36.600
I will personally tell her.

27:42.680 --> 27:45.320
I want you to spread the word for me.

27:45.400 --> 27:46.760
Say that

27:47.280 --> 27:48.800
the girl Sui Yuanqing captured

27:48.880 --> 27:50.680
is my daughter.

27:51.240 --> 27:52.600
I will definitely rescue her.

27:53.400 --> 27:54.440
Marquis.

27:55.480 --> 27:57.320
What do you mean by this?

27:57.400 --> 27:59.280
This is "turning
the enemy's trick against him."

27:59.360 --> 28:00.720
Firstly,

28:00.800 --> 28:03.680
make Sui Yuanqing believe the Marquis
is desperate for his daughter.

28:03.760 --> 28:04.760
He will be reckless and do it alone.

28:04.840 --> 28:05.800
This lowers the enemy‘s guard.

28:06.400 --> 28:07.280
Secondly,

28:07.880 --> 28:10.920
we can let Sui Yuanqing know
he holds a valuable hostage.

28:11.000 --> 28:14.160
The younger girl will not be
in life-threatening danger.

28:15.960 --> 28:17.880
You have a thorough plan.

28:19.200 --> 28:22.240
I entrust the younger Fan girl
to you, Marquis.

28:22.320 --> 28:25.400
Otherwise, I would be too ashamed
to face my old friend.

28:27.320 --> 28:28.520
Rest assured, General.

28:29.400 --> 28:31.160
I will definitely bring her back safely.

28:37.080 --> 28:39.880
Truly, fate toys with people.

28:42.760 --> 28:43.640
General.

28:44.640 --> 28:45.960
Peiyi, come.

28:50.280 --> 28:52.440
There is a matter, heinous,

28:52.520 --> 28:55.720
that may bring the scorn of the world.

28:55.800 --> 28:58.680
Will you do it or not?

28:59.840 --> 29:02.040
My life was saved by you, General.

29:02.560 --> 29:04.280
Every day I live is an extra gift.

29:05.000 --> 29:06.080
What's reputation?

29:06.600 --> 29:07.560
Please speak, General.

29:10.160 --> 29:11.200
Come.

29:15.360 --> 29:18.800
If Prince Changxin's army wants to attack
during the monsoon season,

29:18.880 --> 29:21.120
they will definitely pass through Baxia.

29:25.440 --> 29:28.360
NORTHWEST POST STATION

29:28.440 --> 29:29.400
Beauty Slaughterer!

29:29.480 --> 29:31.280
Beauty Slaughterer, slow down!

29:31.360 --> 29:33.560
-It's on the Chongzhou side, right?
-Yes.

29:33.640 --> 29:35.720
I heard them talk about it
when I was looking for children before.

29:35.800 --> 29:38.560
There is a refugee camp in Baxia,
holding lots of kids.

29:38.640 --> 29:40.000
You should go look there.

29:40.080 --> 29:41.280
See if your sister is there.

29:43.000 --> 29:44.160
Head west, right?

29:44.240 --> 29:46.120
Yes. Go through Baxia, then you'll see it.

29:46.680 --> 29:48.800
JIZHOU PREFECTURAL OFFICE

29:49.400 --> 29:50.920
The matter of Wei Qilin

29:51.000 --> 29:53.800
should be Wei Yan's design
to cover up that year's scandal.

29:53.880 --> 29:55.440
It is to deliberately frame him.

29:55.520 --> 29:56.360
PEACE AND PROSPERITY ALONG THE BORDERS

29:56.440 --> 29:59.280
Wei Yan's character is more than just
power manipulation and autocracy.

29:59.360 --> 30:01.760
He even doesn't hesitate,
for his own selfishness,

30:01.840 --> 30:03.600
to drive loyal generals
and meritorious officials to death.

30:04.200 --> 30:06.520
That’s enough to see his sinister cunning.

30:07.440 --> 30:10.040
Now the war is imminent.

30:10.120 --> 30:13.800
The position of Military Administrator
in the Jizhou army is still vacant.

30:13.880 --> 30:15.320
You can enter the army.

30:15.400 --> 30:16.840
Disintegrate the Wei faction.

30:16.920 --> 30:19.040
After reading this letter, do not delay.

30:19.120 --> 30:21.600
Go to the front lines immediately
to collect the grain.

30:21.680 --> 30:23.080
It will stabilize military morale.

30:23.160 --> 30:25.320
And you can seek a military position.

30:27.640 --> 30:28.480
My Lord.

30:29.000 --> 30:30.040
Mrs. Fan left.

30:30.800 --> 30:32.160
She asked someone to deliver you ten taels

30:32.240 --> 30:33.240
to repay you.

30:33.320 --> 30:35.200
I searched everywhere
but couldn't find her.

30:42.880 --> 30:44.240
I know you want to help Mrs. Fan,

30:44.760 --> 30:45.800
but this war cannot be delayed either.

30:59.200 --> 31:00.040
Master!

31:07.040 --> 31:08.200
Changyu.

31:15.320 --> 31:16.320
My apologies, Miss.

31:16.400 --> 31:17.480
I mistook you for someone.

31:23.840 --> 31:25.360
Leave two people guarding here.

31:25.440 --> 31:27.760
If she returns looking for someone,
tell her my direction.

31:28.520 --> 31:29.360
Yes.

31:37.320 --> 31:38.640
Set out.

31:41.520 --> 31:44.120
JIZHOU PREFECTURAL OFFICE

31:50.880 --> 31:54.120
My lord, the Young Master asked
if you could check on his schoolwork.

31:58.120 --> 31:59.120
Bring him in.

32:02.400 --> 32:04.000
Young Master, come quickly.

32:42.400 --> 32:44.320
What kind of crap is this?

32:44.400 --> 32:46.280
The characters are so weak.

32:47.440 --> 32:48.280
Rewrite.

32:49.000 --> 32:49.840
Dad.

32:50.880 --> 32:52.280
Fa… Father.

32:54.400 --> 32:55.920
If I write it well,

32:56.680 --> 32:59.120
can I go see my mother?

33:00.400 --> 33:01.320
What did you say?

33:03.160 --> 33:04.520
If I write it well,

33:05.800 --> 33:07.720
can I go see my mother?

33:12.520 --> 33:14.240
Who allowed you

33:15.440 --> 33:16.800
to call me father?

33:22.200 --> 33:23.600
Usually,

33:24.680 --> 33:26.560
what does your mom say about your father?

33:27.760 --> 33:29.280
My mother says

33:30.200 --> 33:32.160
Daddy is a great hero.

33:33.000 --> 33:35.520
If one day Bao'er is captured
by bad people,

33:36.480 --> 33:38.440
someone will definitely ask
who your daddy is.

33:38.960 --> 33:42.000
You just tell them
your daddy is a great hero.

33:42.080 --> 33:44.480
Is my daddy really a great hero?

33:44.560 --> 33:45.720
Of course not.

33:47.560 --> 33:50.200
But saying that can save your life.

33:51.000 --> 33:52.640
You must be utterly sincere.

33:52.720 --> 33:55.560
Say your daddy is a great hero. Remember.

33:59.040 --> 34:00.840
This is what your mother
taught you to say, right?

34:03.480 --> 34:05.720
My mother often says this to me.

34:06.640 --> 34:08.199
What else has she said?

34:10.159 --> 34:13.480
Daddy is a great hero who does big things.

34:13.560 --> 34:15.800
He… He loves us very much.

34:17.480 --> 34:20.679
It's just that Daddy also
has to look after this country.

34:20.760 --> 34:23.199
He c-can't come see us often.

34:30.760 --> 34:32.199
Little brat.

34:32.800 --> 34:35.080
Not a word of truth from your mouth.

34:35.679 --> 34:38.040
Your mother is a big liar.

34:38.120 --> 34:40.199
You're a little liar.

34:45.800 --> 34:47.080
But I like hearing it.

34:48.880 --> 34:49.719
Practice your writing.

35:27.400 --> 35:28.240
My lord, spare me!

35:29.520 --> 35:31.040
Drag her out. Beat to death.

35:31.120 --> 35:32.720
-Yes.
-My lord, spare me!

35:32.800 --> 35:34.200
My lord, spare me!

35:34.280 --> 35:35.720
My lord, spare me!

35:37.800 --> 35:39.480
My lord, I was wrong!

35:39.560 --> 35:42.080
My lord, spare me!

35:43.360 --> 35:44.920
I know my wrongdoing.

35:46.080 --> 35:47.400
My lord, spare me!

35:48.040 --> 35:50.040
My lord, spare me!

35:54.040 --> 35:55.640
My lord, spare me!

35:56.560 --> 35:58.520
My lord, spare me!

36:00.880 --> 36:02.320
My lord, spare me!

36:06.240 --> 36:08.200
I won't dare do it again next time!

36:12.080 --> 36:13.520
Bao'er…

36:15.280 --> 36:18.560
My lord, spare me!

36:23.560 --> 36:25.520
My lord, spare me!

36:26.800 --> 36:27.840
Spare me!

36:30.640 --> 36:31.640
My lord!

36:59.120 --> 37:00.280
Is your father

37:01.160 --> 37:02.920
still a great hero?

37:05.600 --> 37:07.680
Daddy is a great hero.

37:07.760 --> 37:09.560
Daddy is a great hero.

37:10.640 --> 37:12.960
Daddy is a great hero.

37:15.520 --> 37:17.160
Daddy is a great hero.

37:20.200 --> 37:21.280
Keep practicing.

37:45.040 --> 37:46.120
It's already spring.

37:46.840 --> 37:48.960
How can the stream be this shallow?

37:53.000 --> 37:54.080
Miss, save me!

37:54.160 --> 37:55.760
Miss, save me!

37:57.320 --> 37:58.160
Miss.

38:02.520 --> 38:03.360
Ran into mountain bandits?

38:06.440 --> 38:08.400
Miss, I'm not a villain.

38:08.920 --> 38:10.320
The government officials
weren't treating us as humans!

38:10.400 --> 38:13.040
They want us citizens to quarry stone
outside the mountains.

38:17.640 --> 38:18.880
I'm going to hide in the woods.

38:18.960 --> 38:20.080
Don't tell my whereabouts.

38:20.160 --> 38:21.200
I have a whole family to raise.

38:21.280 --> 38:22.640
If they capture me,

38:22.720 --> 38:24.840
I probably won't survive

38:34.120 --> 38:35.160
Halt.

38:35.240 --> 38:37.440
Miss, did you see a man pass by?

38:38.480 --> 38:39.960
-Yes.
-Which way did he go?

38:41.000 --> 38:42.080
This one.

38:45.920 --> 38:47.600
You two, continue pursuit along that road.

38:48.200 --> 38:49.960
-The rest, come with me.
-Yes.

39:02.480 --> 39:04.640
I thank you on behalf
of my whole family, Miss.

39:04.720 --> 39:05.680
Thank you, Miss.

39:05.760 --> 39:06.760
Thank you, Miss.

39:11.280 --> 39:12.440
It was nothing.

39:12.960 --> 39:13.880
No need for thanks.

39:14.560 --> 39:16.720
Miss, any more food?

39:16.800 --> 39:19.360
I haven't eaten in days.

39:20.640 --> 39:21.720
I'll get it for you.

39:45.160 --> 39:46.160
Sneak attacking me!

39:46.240 --> 39:47.640
Do you think I'm easy to bully?

39:47.720 --> 39:48.720
You…

39:48.800 --> 39:50.080
When did you figure it out?

39:50.160 --> 39:52.280
There is the sound of metal clashing
from your sleeve.

39:52.360 --> 39:53.600
Clearly a dagger.

39:53.680 --> 39:55.000
You definitely wanted to take my horse

39:55.600 --> 39:56.600
and escape.

40:02.840 --> 40:03.800
-Hyah!
-Halt.

40:07.320 --> 40:08.640
Why did you lie to me?

40:08.720 --> 40:11.160
Officer, just now,
I was tricked by this person.

40:11.240 --> 40:12.800
He said he had a whole family to raise.

40:12.880 --> 40:14.680
He wanted me to hide
his whereabouts for him.

40:14.760 --> 40:16.680
Just now, he still wanted to do me harm.

40:16.760 --> 40:17.840
I subdued him.

40:18.640 --> 40:20.280
Tie them both up. Take them both away.

40:21.680 --> 40:23.360
Officer, I was wronged!

40:23.440 --> 40:25.080
Just now, I didn't know the situation.

40:25.600 --> 40:27.440
But then I subdued him again.

40:27.520 --> 40:28.440
Consider it making up for my mistake.

40:28.520 --> 40:29.440
Spare me from punishment.

40:29.520 --> 40:31.720
He's a Chongzhou scout.

40:31.800 --> 40:34.720
Who knows if you aren't
a Chongzhou rebel too?

40:34.800 --> 40:37.200
Seeing you couldn't take this scout,

40:37.280 --> 40:38.800
then you acted out this play together.

40:40.680 --> 40:42.200
I have household registration documents.

40:43.120 --> 40:45.400
Officer, I'm from Jizhou.

40:49.600 --> 40:51.440
Since you're from Jizhou,

40:51.960 --> 40:53.360
now right in the middle of war,

40:54.120 --> 40:56.480
why are you running towards Chongzhou?

41:00.040 --> 41:01.800
We are not here to verify your identity.

41:01.880 --> 41:03.720
It can wait until we return.

41:04.480 --> 41:05.680
Take them away.

41:06.280 --> 41:07.120
Move.

43:44.960 --> 43:48.680
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

43:48.760 --> 43:49.640
Subtitle Translation by: Peng Peng
